{"tid":1612384,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭戰術（一）","createTime":"2019-10-02T08:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:58.000Z","uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"398e0aa28c4b462160fd29ad356434ae36e948be","tid":1612384,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:43:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ACDNGA8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FACDNGA8.jpg&h=ddb3a209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作用 前線做完野<br />\n佢地可以退返人群<br />\n黑警沖埋去既將會係面對我地普通市民<br />\n如果大家企硬既話 係唔需要驚佢地<br />\n因為捉左都告唔入<br />\n另外因為大家站硬 堅守陣線 其實係有機會反打<br />\n只要大家保留空間比前線做完野<br />\n有空間比佢地退返入去<br />\n <br />\n所以係時候放棄全民黑杉<br />\n有新戰術再補充"},{"pid":"74673f333662defcee5658f63dc5c803c939dcbc","tid":1612384,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"push?"},{"pid":"e7372e7433ea1ae74db813b51519d95ea6e833e5","tid":1612384,"uid":183752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T08:45:42.000Z","msg":"push!"},{"pid":"a3b528637962d7c64e3b239c8e842866a53e6663","tid":1612384,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T15:44:58.000Z","msg":"銀髮軍師 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非</span>加入 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">戰況大增千倍</span>的新戰術<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1613583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1613583</a>"}]}